.DS_Store

# Obsidian per-machine state (keep shared config, ignore local workspace/cache)
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/cache
.obsidian/plugins/
.obsidian/themes/

# Local-only personal-vault mount(s) — never commit private KB into this PUBLIC repo.
# See docs/design/vault-docs-reconciliation.md: mount direction is public docs/ → private
# vault, never the reverse. These reserve the in-tree paths so an accidental private-vault
# symlink here can't be committed.
/.vault/
/vault-mount/

# Pure-generated capability docs — regenerated on demand from sux/src/fns/*.ts
# (`npm run docs` → FUNCTIONS.md; `npm run wiki` → llms.txt). Nothing imports or
# bundles them: `/llms.txt` is served live from the registry (renderOverview in
# observability.ts), and FUNCTIONS.md is a human/skill reference. Committing them
# caused every concurrent PR to collide on these files; they are no longer tracked.
# (Contrast sux/src/fns/index.ts, which IS bundled into the Worker and stays committed.)
/llms.txt
/sux/FUNCTIONS.md
